# Stamena - Figma Implementation Checklist

## How to Use This Checklist
1. Open Figma design alongside your app
2. For each screen, verify EVERY element matches
3. Check off items only when pixel-perfect
4. Take screenshots for comparison
5. Note any discrepancies in "Issues" column

---

