## ANIMATIONS CHECKLIST

### Critical Animations (Must be 60fps)

#### Onboarding Graph
- [ ] Path draws smoothly (1200ms)
- [ ] Dot moves along curve (1500ms)
- [ ] Gradient transitions cleanly
- [ ] Text reveals sequentially (300ms stagger)
- [ ] No frame drops
- [ ] Smooth on device

**FPS Test**: _____ (must be 60)
