## GENERAL UI/UX CHECKLIST

### Typography
- [ ] All headings correct size/weight
- [ ] Body text readable
- [ ] Captions appropriate size
- [ ] Line heights match Figma
- [ ] Text alignment correct
- [ ] Color contrast sufficient

**Issues**: _______________________

### Colors
- [ ] Primary red exact match (#FF4444)
- [ ] Background dark matches
- [ ] All gradients accurate
- [ ] Text colors correct
- [ ] Success green matches
- [ ] All colors from theme

**Issues**: _______________________

### Spacing
- [ ] Screen padding consistent (20px)
- [ ] Card padding correct (16px)
- [ ] Element gaps appropriate (12px)
- [ ] All spacing from theme constants

**Issues**: _______________________

### Buttons
- [ ] Height correct (56px)
- [ ] Border radius matches (12px)
- [ ] Press animation (scale/opacity)
- [ ] Loading states
- [ ] Disabled states
- [ ] Shadow/elevation

**Issues**: _______________________

### Icons
- [ ] All icons from correct library
- [ ] Correct sizes
- [ ] Proper alignment
- [ ] Color matches context

**Issues**: _______________________

### Images
- [ ] High quality (not pixelated)
- [ ] Correct aspect ratios
- [ ] Loading states
- [ ] Caching enabled
- [ ] Progressive loading

**Issues**: _______________________

