## PERFORMANCE CHECKLIST

### App Launch
- [ ] Launches in < 2s
- [ ] No white flash
- [ ] Smooth splash transition

**Time**: _____ seconds

### Navigation
- [ ] Screen transitions < 200ms
- [ ] No jank
- [ ] Preserves state
- [ ] Back navigation smooth

**Time per transition**: _____ ms

### Lists
- [ ] Smooth scrolling (60fps)
- [ ] Virtualization enabled
- [ ] No blank items
- [ ] Pull to refresh works

**FPS**: _____

### API Calls
- [ ] Loading states shown
- [ ] Error states handled
- [ ] Optimistic updates
- [ ] Response time acceptable

**Avg time**: _____ ms

### Memory
- [ ] No memory leaks
- [ ] Images release properly
- [ ] Total usage < 150MB

**Usage**: _____ MB

