## DEVICE TESTING

### iPhone Testing
- [ ] iPhone 13/14/15 (standard)
- [ ] iPhone 13/14/15 Pro Max (large)
- [ ] iPhone SE (small)
- [ ] Safe area handling
- [ ] Notch handling

### Android Testing
- [ ] Pixel/Samsung (if applicable)
- [ ] Different screen sizes
- [ ] Navigation bar handling

### Orientations
- [ ] Portrait (primary)
- [ ] Landscape locked (if needed)

---

## ACCESSIBILITY

- [ ] Font scaling works
- [ ] Screen reader labels
- [ ] Color contrast WCAG AA
- [ ] Touch targets ≥ 44x44
- [ ] Reduced motion support

---

## FINAL REVIEW

### Before Sprint Demo
- [ ] All screens pixel-perfect
- [ ] All animations 60fps
- [ ] No console errors
- [ ] No TypeScript errors
- [ ] Git committed and pushed
- [ ] Screenshots taken
- [ ] Video recording prepared

### Before App Store
- [ ] All checklists complete
- [ ] Founders approved
- [ ] Testing complete
- [ ] Performance targets met
- [ ] No critical bugs

---

## Notes Section

Use this space for:
- Design decisions
- Deviations from Figma (with justification)
- Performance optimizations
- Known issues to fix

